"https://www.salesforce.com/etc/designs/blogsRedesign/images/default.jpg", "og:site_name": "Salesforce", "og:url": "https://www.salesforce.com/solutions/industries/manufacturing/overview/", "og:type": "website", "og:locale": "en_us", "body_text": "\n             \n                \n                    Manufacturing \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n                     Overview \n                    \n                 \n                     Products \n                    \n                 \n                     Rebate Management \n                    \n                 \n                     Customer Stories \n                    \n                 \n                     Pricing \n                    \n                 \n                     FAQ \n                    \n                 \n                     Resources \n                    \n                 QUESTIONS? \n                CALL US\n             \n                1-800-667-6389\n             Questions? \n                CALL US\n             \n                1-800-720-0371\n             DISCOVER TRAILHEAD. \n THE FUN WAY TO LEARN SALESFORCE. \n              \n                start learning\n              \n              \n             Watch the Keynote: Connect the Value Chain, at Dreamforce \u201922.\u00a0 WATCH FOR FREE \u00a0> GET TOGETHER, SAFELY WITH SAFETY CLOUD.  LEARN MORE \u00a0> GET TOGETHER, SAFELY WITH SAFETY CLOUD.  LEARN MORE \u00a0> \n                \n                    SALESFORCE FOR MANUFACTURING \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n                \n                    Connect the value chain. \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n              \n                Learn more\n              \n              \n             \n              \n                See the Fike story\n               \n              \n             \n                \n                    SALESFORCE FOR MANUFACTURING \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n                \n                    Connect the value chain. \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n              \n                Learn more\n              \n              \n             \n                \n                    Transform the future of manufacturing customer operations with AI + DATA + CRM. \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n                \n                    Manufacturing Cloud \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n                \n                    Starting at $375 USD per user per month* (billed annually) \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n              \n                Get The Datasheet\n              \n              \n             \n              \n                Learn More\n               \n              \n             \n                \n                    Rebate Management \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n              \n                Watch Demo\n              \n              \n             \n              \n                Learn More\n               \n              \n             \n                \n                    Solve manufacturers\u2019 greatest challenges with intelligent cloud solutions. \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n                \n                    Solution \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n                \n                    Modernize Commercial Operations \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n              \n                Watch Demo\n              \n              \n             \n              \n                Get the Guide\n               \n              \n             Manufacturing Cloud  helps your business connect sales and operations to drive forecast accuracy and visibility across your ecosystem. Rebate Management  lets you build, manage, and analyze incentive programs within the CRM to drive channel sales and loyalty. Revenue Cloud  is a revenue management platform that helps automate the product-to-cash journey. B2B Commerce  allows you to unlock self-service revenue channels, connect every buyer touchpoint, and launch personalized experiences fast. CRM Analytics  delivers actionable insights throughout the entire sales and revenue cycle. Slack  connects your manufacturing value chain in a single, collaborative workspace. MuleSoft Anypoint Platform  lets you integrate data from any system to deliver critical, time-sensitive projects \u2014 all with a single platform for APIs and integrations. \u201c With Salesforce, we expect to use these capabilities to help deepen our relationship and collaboration with our customers.\u201d \n              \n                See the Story\n              \n              \n             \n                \n                    SOLUTION \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n                \n                    Transform the Service Experience \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n              \n                Watch Demo\n              \n              \n             \n              \n                GET THE GUIDE\n               \n              \n             Sevice Cloud  allows you to streamline your processes, automate your workflows, capture customer feedback, and deploy the right agent at the right time. Field Service  automates field operations including mobile inventory management, vehicle tracking, scheduling, customer portals, and more. Experience Cloud  lets you quickly launch data-powered sites, portals, and apps, connected across the customer journey. MuleSoft Anypoint Platform  lets you integrate data from any system to deliver critical, time-sensitive projects \u2014 all with a single platform for APIs and integrations. Slack  connects your manufacturing value chain in a single, collaborative workspace. CRM Analytics  helps your entire team find important answers and start making data-driven decisions. Salesforce Feedback Management  automates the timely capture of feedback and insights that drive continuous improvement of the customer experience. \u201c We chose Salesforce Field Service because we knew it could provide a central platform to unify service and sales data while providing the infrastructure to scale for our future endeavors\u201d \n              \n                See the Story\n              \n              \n             \n                \n                    SOLUTION \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n                \n                    Simplify Partner Engagement \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n              \n                Watch Demos\n              \n              \n             \n              \n                Get the Guide\n               \n              \n             Manufacturing Cloud  helps your business connect sales and operations to drive forecast accuracy and visibility across your ecosystem. Experience Cloud  lets you quickly launch data-powered sites, portals, and apps, connected across the customer journey. CRM Analytics  delivers actionable insights throughout the entire sales and revenue cycle. Rebate Management  lets you build, manage, and analyze incentive programs within the CRM to drive channel sales and loyalty. Loyalty Management  lets you build intelligent B2B and B2C loyalty programs that are flexible, configurable, and rapidly deployable Revenue Cloud  is a revenue management platform that helps automate the product-to-cash journey. B2B Commerce  allows you to unlock self-service revenue channels, connect every buyer touchpoint, and launch personalized experiences fast. Marketing Cloud  lets you personalize customer experiences and optimize each campaign with data-first enterprise solutions for any channel and device. Slack  connects your manufacturing value chain in a single, collaborative workspace. MuleSoft Anypoint Platform  lets you integrate data from any system to deliver critical, time-sensitive projects \u2014 all with a single platform for APIs and integrations. \u201c Schneider Electric powers a global workforce for a sustainable world. \u201cFor a company like us, it\u2019s a revolution\u201d \n              \n                See the Story\n              \n              \n             \n                \n                    SOLUTION \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n                \n                    Channel Incentive Management \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n              \n                Watch Demo\n              \n              \n             Manufacturing Cloud , our manufacturing CRM, helps you improve business agility, empower your teams with data, and achieve commercial excellence. Loyalty Management \u00a0lets you build intelligent B2B and B2C loyalty programs that are flexible, configurable, and rapidly deployable. Rebate Management \u00a0lets you build, manage, and analyze incentive programs in the CRM to drive channel sales and loyalty. CRM Analytics \u00a0delivers actionable insights throughout the entire sales and revenue cycle. Experience Cloud \u00a0lets you quickly launch data-powered sites, portals, and apps, connected across the customer journey. \n              \n                See the Story\n               \n              \n             \n                \n      