d Flexible Implementation \n                \n                \n                \n                \n            \n            \n            \n        \n    @@\n        \n        \n            \n            \n                \n            \n            \n            \n            \n                \n                    Tailored to your Business \n                \n                \n                \n                \n            \n            \n            \n        \n    @@\n        \n        \n            \n            \n                \n            \n            \n            \n            \n                \n                    Best Practices for Success \n                \n                \n                \n                \n            \n            \n            \n        \n    @@\n        \n        \n            \n            \n                \n            \n            \n            \n            \n                \n                    Sales Cloud \n                \n                \n                \n                \n            \n            \n            \n        \n    @@\n        \n        \n            \n            \n                \n            \n            \n            \n            \n                \n                    Service Cloud \n                \n                \n                \n                \n            \n            \n            \n        \n    @@\n        \n        \n            \n            \n                \n            \n            \n            \n            \n                \n                    Marketing Cloud Account Engagement \n                \n                \n                \n                \n            \n            \n            \n        \n    ", "canonical": "https://www.salesforce.com/form/contact/starter-pack/", "og:title": "Salesforce CRM Starter Pack", "og:description": "The CRM Starter Pack is the fast way to customize and implement Salesforce to help your unique business \u2014 and start seeing value.", "og:image": "https://www.salesforce.com/content/dam/web/en_ca/www/images/hp/recommended-for-you-starter-pack.jpg", "og:site_name": "Salesforce.com", "og:url": "https://www.salesforce.com/form/contact/starter-pack/", "og:type": "website", "og:locale": "en_us", "body_text": "\n                \n                    Maximize savings with the CRM Starter Pack \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             Save up to 40% with the CRM Starter Pack and get started with Salesforce now. Find the tools you need to build stronger customer relationships. Salesforce offers solutions that help: Reach your audience with personalized content \n Increase sales productivity with automations \n Connect with customers across channels \n Get 1-to-1 support and guidance from Salesforce experts with up to  40% savings  by starting with the  CRM Starter Pack . \n                \n                    Fill out this quick form for us to schedule a call with you. \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             Enter your first name Enter your last name Enter your title Enter a valid email address Enter your company name Select the number of employees Enter a valid phone number Select your country Select your state/province \n          This is a required field\n       Please Complete Captcha \n                \n                    Jet It increased its sales revenue 300% YoY with Salesforce. \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n        \n        \n            \n            \n                \n            \n            \n            \n             \n                \n                    \u201cWe are in an industry where failure is not an option. We didn\u2019t have time for a misstep, so it was smart to leverage the CRM Starter Pack to ensure we were off and running from day one with our integration with Salesforce.\u201d \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n            \n            \n        \n     \n        \n        \n            \n            \n                \n            \n            \n            \n             \n                \n                    Glenn Gonzales \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n            \n            \n        \n     \n        \n        \n            \n            \n                \n            \n            \n            \n             \n                \n                    Founder & CEO, Jet It \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n            \n            \n        \n     \n        \n        \n            \n            \n                \n            \n            \n            \n             \n                \n                    \u201cWe can\u2019t lose sight of any leads \u2014 it\u2019s imperative that we stay engaged with our prospects. Salesforce provides us with that platform to communicate with our customers.\u201d \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n            \n            \n        \n     \n        \n        \n            \n            \n                \n            \n            \n            \n             \n                \n                    Henry Kim \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n            \n            \n        \n     \n        \n        \n            \n            \n                \n            \n            \n            \n             \n                \n                    COO, Jet It \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n            \n            \n        \n     \n                \n                    Get started with Salesforce in a snap. \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n        \n        \n            \n            \n                \n            \n            \n            \n             \n                \n                    We know you want to see value from Salesforce fast \u2013 and you want to get your platform set up right the first time around. That's where the CRM Starter Pack can help. \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n            \n            \n        \n     \n                \n                    How it Works \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n                \n                    Quick and Flexible Implementation \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             Deploy Salesforce within weeks by meeting with our experts, who can help you maximize efficiency. \n                \n                    Tailored to your Business \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             Configure your end-to-end business and processes. And increase team efficiency with guidance and setup. \n                \n                    Best Practices for Success \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             Get your team up to speed with guided walkthroughs, as well as 30, 60, and 90-day recommendations. \n                \n                    You can mix and match solutions for Sales, Service, and Marketing \u2015 one or all. \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n                \n                    No matter what you choose, the CRM Starter Pack is customized to your specific needs with the inclusive Jump Start Implementation service. \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n                \n                    Sales Cloud \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n        \n  