ms a user-friendly platform . Track and analyze user feedback . \n                \n                    1. Build close relationships with your customers. \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \u201c Salesforce Essentials gives us everything we need \u2014 and nothing we don\u2019t.\u201d  |\n            \n                Co-Founder & CEO, Humu \n            \n         \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n              \n                Engage with customers and manage relationships with Salesforce Essentials\n               \n              \n             \n                \n                    2. Give your teams a user-friendly platform. \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n              \n                Grow your skills with Trailhead\n               \n              \n             \n                \n                    3. Track and analyze user feedback. \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \u201c That\u2019s the kind of data-driven approach we can take because of Salesforce Essentials.\u201d  |\n            \n                Head of Strategic Accounts and Partnerships, Humu \n            \n         \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n              \n                Gain comprehensive customer insights with Einstein Activity Capture\n               \n              \n             \n                \n                    Ready to build a single view of your customer? \n                \n                \n                \n                \n             \n              \n                Get started with Customer 360\n               \n              \n             \n                \n                    Related Content \n           